comment: Lee (SAS) makes incidental contact with Temple (SAC) during the loose ball.
Evans (SAC) drives into Ginobili (SAS), who establishes a legal guarding position at the time of the contact.
Simmons (SAS) makes contact with Evans (SAC) that affects his SQBR.
Evans (SAC) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Murray (SAS) that does not affect his SQBR.
Evans (SAC) legally contests Ginobili's (SAS) driving shot attempt and the contact is incidental.
Green (SAS) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Evans (SAC) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Lawson (SAC) makes incidental contact with Mills (SAS) that does not affect his SQBR.
Temple (SAC) commits a take foul on Murray (SAS).
Murray (SAS) makes marginal contact with Lawson (SAC) that does not affect his SQBR.
